title: Aruba Networks Wireless LAN Controller (WLC): Connected WLAN Accesspoints
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/network/aruba
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors

 - the state

 - the accespoint group

 - the system location

 of an Aruba Networks WLAN Controller Accesspoint.

 The service goes

 - {CRIT} if an accesspoint goes down

 - {WARN} if the accespoint is inactive

 - {OK} in all other cases

 The check uses the WLSX-SYSTEMEXT-MIB

item:
 The WLAN accesspoint name.

discovery:
 One service is created for each provisioned access point.
